data.description: Gorgeous 2-story 5 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms w/ two car garage & an extended front terrace. Upon entry into the foyer you will be amazed w/ the open space & 9ft ceilings. Neutral tile floors throughout the first floor, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, spacious pantry. Large backyard w/ a paved covered terrace & enclosed privacy fence w/ no neighbors beyond the fence line. Second floor has rug throughout, a full size laundry room, & 2nd bathroom w/ dual sinks, extended mirror, separate entrance to toilet, shower & tub. Master bedroom w/ walk in closet, his & hers sinks, glass door standing shower, & bath tub. Community has a state of the art club house, which includes a park, splashpad for the kids, BBQ area, gym & trails throughout the community for walking, cycling, and jogging.
